Phase 1 – Project Initialization & First Visible UI
- Verified Next.js shell, dashboard, and routing in place
- Connected to Neon Postgres (`SELECT 1`)
- Added UI scaffolding and startup logics for Phase 2 handoff
- Deployed to Vercel (production URL live)

Phase 3 – Authentication & Identity
- Implemented DB-backed sessions with secure cookies
- Added registration/login/logout flows with bcryptjs hashing
- Wired role-aware nav and dashboards (learner/instructor/admin)
- Seed endpoint added for demo accounts

Phase 4 – Role-Aware Dashboards & Courses
- Added courses schema and instructor-only course creation
- Role-aware dashboards: instructors see owned courses, admins see all courses, learners see empty state
- Course detail pages render real data
- Deployed successfully with course creation validated

Phase 5 – Enrollment
- Added enrollments join table with uniqueness
- Enrollment server action for admin/owners; learner email validation
- Learner dashboard shows enrolled courses; course access gated by enrollment/ownership/admin
- Instructors/Admins can view enrolled learners and enroll by email on course pages
- Deployed successfully

Phase 6 – Course Content (Modules & Items)
- Added modules and content items with ordered insertion
- Instructors/Admins can add modules and content (page/link) per course
- Learners see modules/items when enrolled; access guards enforced
- Content item pages support in-module next/prev navigation
- Deployed successfully

Admin Roster
- Added admin-only roster view and nav link
- Admins can add users (email/password/role) and delete users (self-delete blocked)
- Deployed successfully

Admin Course Management
- Moved course creation to Courses page; admin-only with instructor assignment
- Added admin edit/delete course controls; instructors see only assigned courses
- Switched to Neon serverless DB client for stability
- Deployed successfully
Admin UX Updates
- Restricted guest nav to login; admins land on Admin dashboard
- Added admin-only Enroll menu to enroll learners into courses
- Added simple admin dashboard with course list
- Deployed successfully
Instructor UX Updates
- Simplified instructor dashboard layout and nav
- Added modules management page with view/create/edit/delete
- Added content management page with view/create/edit/delete
- Courses page links inline tabs for Modules and Content
Fixes
- Admin nav simplified (Admin, Course, Logout) with tabs for Modules/Content accessible from Course
- Enrollments grouped by course on admin enroll page for clarity

